35814 | 2025-05-15 14:22:15,955 | üü£ critical | main_func | main.py:12 | Critical message using logab's log_init()
35814 | 2025-05-15 14:22:15,955 | üü¢ debug    | main_func | main.py:14 | Debug message using print()
